					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2265635#post-2812160</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2265635/scp-3104#post-2812160</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 06 May 2017 00:06:22 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>atomicthumbs</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>303535</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is SCP-3104, a cops magnet.</p> <p>It's very illegal. Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2005044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1494029988" alt="Decibelles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2005044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" >Decibelles</a></span> for feedback, to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aiden-eldritch" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1494029988" alt="Aiden Eldritch" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aiden-eldritch" >Aiden Eldritch</a></span> for helping me realize that the item I was describing was a cops magnet to go along with my <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-555">corpse magnet</a>, and to The Government for <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Brownsville_Port_of_Entry_CBP_Officers_Seize_$92,820_in_Cocaine_at_Brownsville_%26_Matamoros_International_Bridge_(26095279700).jpg">the source image</a>, which is in the public domain.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
